<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要和你比坐禅。”虎力大仙说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁一动不动地坐得时间最长，谁就赢了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我过去经常坐禅。”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我最近没坐过，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我没办法一动不动地坐着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧上前一步说：“我和你比。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，你确定？”悟净问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧点点头说：“我坐禅坐了很多年了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这次比赛对我来说很容易。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不是普通的坐禅比赛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要在空中坐禅。你可以吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59695</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，唐僧看上去有点儿紧张了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还没来得及回答，悟空拍了拍他的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我师父没问题。”悟空回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在唐僧耳边低声说：“别担心，师父。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80642</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你只管坐禅。其他的事情我来处理。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们还在说什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙说，“我们开始吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙和唐僧走到了法坛中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们盘腿坐下，手掌向上，放在腿上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们闭上了眼睛，开始坐禅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100570</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，虎力大仙慢慢升到了空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父不会那个。他会输的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心。”悟空说，“我会帮助他的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空念了个咒语，朝着唐僧吹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧从地上升了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼睛依然紧闭着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他就升到了虎力大仙的旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得师父会赢的。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也很会坐禅。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我应该和他比一比。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要抬起你可是要费很多法力的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父的脸动了。”悟净突然说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊。”八戒说，“出什么事了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能他头痛吧。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这可怎么办。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果师父动了，他就会输的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抬头看着唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得他身体痒痒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空说，“在这等着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空隐身飞到了唐僧那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有个跳蚤在唐僧的头上爬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”悟空想，“唐僧头上为什么会有跳蚤？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他连头发都没有。”悟空咬了一下嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“虎力大仙一定是用了法术。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是他把这跳蚤放在了这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那可恶的骗子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空赶走了跳蚤并挠了挠唐僧的头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧的脸不再动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我要教训一下虎力大仙。”悟空想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拔了根毫毛，变出了一只蜈蚣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把蜈蚣扔到了虎力大仙的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蜈蚣爬过了虎力大仙的耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的耳朵动了动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，蜈蚣沿着虎力大仙的嘴巴爬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙动了动嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鼻子也动了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，那蜈蚣爬到虎力大仙的鼻子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虎力大仙打了个喷嚏，然后……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”虎力大仙大叫，“有东西咬我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他无法专注坐禅，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261556</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从空中掉下来摔在地上，尘土飞扬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时候，地上出现了一只死老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和唐僧也回到了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>周围的人们都不说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士们和和尚们互相看了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空清了清嗓子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那虎力大仙其实是个邪恶的老虎精。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在他死了，我希望你们能互相帮助，和平相处。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>